data.title: Quiz App
data.subtitle: Java Quiz App with a web module
data.description: Features : * Chapter wise complete Java Tutorials* Programs for better understanding (100+ programs)* Output for each program * Categorized Questions and Answers* Practice Quiz* Very simple User Interface* One click share (Tutorials and Programs)* Daily updating contents of app*And Much More!*Daily adding new questions,programs,quiz* Any one can take a short test and check their programming skills.* It helps new Java and Android developer to increase their java programming skill.* Unlimited Access throughout the app* Offline Mode*New features coming soon..The Java programming language requires the presence of a software platform in order for compiled programs to be executed.
